==Bariai==

===Etymology===
From Proto-Ngero *''i-om'' (compare {{etyl|mmt|-}} ''yu''), although the precise form of this word, like {{etyl|kvc|-}} and {{etyl|khl|-}} ''[[veao]]'', is unexplained.<ref>{{R:poz-oce:Ross 1988}}, page 164: PNg *''i-om'' > Malai ''yom'', Gitua ''yum'', Malalamai ''yu'' (the forms Kove ''veao'' and Bariai ''eau'' are unexplained).</ref>

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ËˆeÉ‘u/|[ËˆeÌ¯É‘uÌ¯]|lang=bch}}

===Noun===
{{head|bch|noun}}

# [[water]]

====Derived terms====
* {{l|bch|eau-eai||in the water}} {{IPAchar|/eÉ‘u.eÉ‘i/|[ËˆeÌ¯É‘uÌ¯.iÌ¯É‘iÌ¯]|lang=bch}}

