===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|hâ‚‚wehâ‚}}
From {{inh|en|enm|air|air, eir|gas, atmosphere}}, from {{der|en|xno|[[aeir]], [[eyer]]}}, {{der|en|fro|[[aire]], [[eir]]}}, from {{der|en|la|ÄÄ“r}}, from {{der|en|grc|á¼€Î®Ï||wind, atmosphere}}. Displaced native {{cog|enm|luft|luft, lift|air}} (from {{cog|ang|lyft||air, atmosphere}}), {{cog|enm|loft||air, upper region}} (from {{cog|non|lopt||air, sky, loft}}). More at [[lift]], [[loft]].

